---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Alumni Hall · Old Toby Academy"
  description="Alumni Hall — the post-graduation community for continuing education, custom MIDI requests, and the spring concert showcase."
  activeNav="alumni"
  footerVariant="short"
>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="page-head">
      <div class="eyebrow">For Those Who Have Graduated</div>
      <h1>Alumni Hall</h1>
      <p class="kicker">An extension of the Academy for those who have completed both terms — a place to keep teaching one another, to ask after a stuck note, to gather a band, to commission a midi, or simply to sit by the fire and trade ideas.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hall-grid">

      <!-- Notice Board -->
      <section class="board">
        <h2>The Notice Board</h2>
        <p class="board-sub">Open posts from the Hall, most recent first.</p>

        <article class="post">
          <span class="post-tag band">BAND</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Looking for a fiddler &amp; harp for a Bree-land set</h4>
            <p>Forming a small ensemble for the Spring concert at the green. Three pieces, gentle pace, room to flourish. A Lonely Mountain fiddle would be a joy.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="green">a green name</span><br />
            2 days ago<br />
            6 replies
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="post">
          <span class="post-tag req">REQ</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Custom midi: 6-part arrangement of a sea-shanty?</h4>
            <p>Has anyone the time to set this up? Lead, two harmonies, two strings and drums. Happy to pay in pints at the Pony.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="green">a green name</span><br />
            5 days ago<br />
            2 replies
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="post">
          <span class="post-tag help">HELP</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Drums overwhelming the lead — Reaper question</h4>
            <p>Followed Precept the Fifth (separate the drums). Still bleeding into the melody on the louder pads. Anyone fought this with success?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="green">a green name</span><br />
            1 week ago<br />
            11 replies
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="post">
          <span class="post-tag idea">IDEA</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Periodic project: a class band tribute</h4>
            <p>What if every two months we set a song and each cohort submits an arrangement? Cross-cohort listening party at the end. Just a thought.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="green">a green name</span><br />
            2 weeks ago<br />
            18 replies
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="post">
          <span class="post-tag help">HELP</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Out-of-range notes on a Sprightly Fiddle</h4>
            <p>Range starts at G1 — anything below cuts. What's the cleanest workaround without losing the line entirely?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="green">a green name</span><br />
            3 weeks ago<br />
            7 replies
          </div>
        </article>

      </section>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div>
          <h3>What the Hall is for</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Continued education</li>
            <li>Troubleshooting existing problems</li>
            <li>Requests to join concert bands</li>
            <li>Requests for custom-made midi files</li>
            <li>Periodic projects to maintain skills</li>
            <li>Free exchange of ideas</li>
            <li>Opportunity to join advanced training</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Joining the Hall</h3>
          <p class="small">If you agree to abide by the rules below and contribute to a positive community experience, message a faculty member by direct message and access will be granted.</p>
          <form class="access-form" name="alumni-access" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/thanks">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="alumni-access" />
            <p hidden><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
            <label>Character name<input type="text" name="character" required /></label>
            <label>Server<input type="text" name="server" /></label>
            <label>How to reach you<input type="text" name="contact" required placeholder="email or in-game" /></label>
            <label>A few words on why<textarea name="note" rows="3"></textarea></label>
            <button class="btn btn-ghost" type="submit">Send Request</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Today in the Hall</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="smallcaps">Open requests</span> · 12</li>
            <li><span class="smallcaps">Active bands</span> · 4</li>
            <li><span class="smallcaps">Pieces in review</span> · 7</li>
            <li><span class="smallcaps">Members</span> · 38</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <!-- Concert Showcase -->
    <section class="concert">
      <div class="concert-head">
        <div class="eyebrow">The Final Recital</div>
        <h2>Class Band — The Spring Concert</h2>
        <p class="kicker">Each graduating cohort is encouraged to put on a concert showcasing what they have learned. Below: the program of the latest recital, kept in the archives.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="program">
        <div class="program-head">
          <div class="crest-mini">❦</div>
          <h3>The Spring Programme</h3>
          <div class="meta">at the green of Bree · seven o'clock · the realm's reckoning</div>
        </div>

        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">I.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">Big Iron <em>after Marty Robbins · 6 parts</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">3:24</span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">II.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">Tell It Like It Is <em>after Aaron Neville · 10 parts</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">3:18</span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">III.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">Beth <em>after KISS · 6 parts, flute change</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">2:42</span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">IV.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">Coraz&oacute;n Espinado <em>after Santana · 12 parts, with drums</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">4:12</span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">— intermission —</span>
          <span class="pgm-title"></span>
          <span class="pgm-time"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">V.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">Load Out / Stay <em>after Jackson Browne · 11 parts</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">9:35</span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">VI.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">We Didn't Start the Fire <em>after Billy Joel · ensemble</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">4:42</span>
        </div>
        <div class="program-piece">
          <span class="pgm-num">VII.</span>
          <span class="pgm-title">Cavatina <em>encore · 6 parts</em></span>
          <span class="pgm-time">3:30</span>
        </div>

        <div class="program-foot">
          Performed by the graduating cohort.<br />
          Conducted by the Master of Recitals.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Rules of Conduct -->
    <section class="rules">
      <div class="eyebrow">House Rules</div>
      <h2>Rules of Conduct</h2>
      <p class="muted italic">The Hall is for everyone, and is kept that way by everyone.</p>
      <div class="rules-grid">
        <div>
          <h4>I. STAY ON TOPIC</h4>
          <p>Posts in the channel they belong; conversations not hijacked.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>II. CONSTRUCTIVE CRITICISM</h4>
          <p>Feedback is offered with an alternative attached. Negativity without solution is not feedback.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>III. RESPECTFUL COMMUNICATION</h4>
          <p>No personal attacks, no harassment. Polite language at all times.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>IV. APPROPRIATE LANGUAGE</h4>
          <p>No profanity. A tone suitable for all ages and backgrounds.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>V. ENGAGE POSITIVELY</h4>
          <p>Encourage one another. Foster a welcoming, inclusive environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>ENFORCEMENT</h4>
          <p>Violations may result in warnings, post deletions, or bans, depending on severity. Decisions by moderators are final.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  .page-head { padding: 56px 0 24px; border-bottom: 1px double var(--rule); margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .page-head h1 { font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }

  .hall-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 48px; margin-top: 24px; }

  .board {
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 14px, rgba(31, 58, 46, 0.025) 14px, rgba(31, 58, 46, 0.025) 28px),
      rgba(255, 250, 235, 0.4);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .board::before { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--rule-soft); pointer-events: none; }
  .board h2 { font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .board .board-sub { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .post {
    padding: 22px 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr auto;
    gap: 16px; align-items: start;
  }
  .post:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .post-tag {
    font-family: var(--display); letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 8px; border: 1px solid;
    align-self: start; text-align: center; line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .post-tag.req { color: var(--oxblood); border-color: var(--oxblood); }
  .post-tag.band { color: var(--forest-deep); border-color: var(--forest-deep); }
  .post-tag.help { color: #8a6e1d; border-color: #8a6e1d; }
  .post-tag.idea { color: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); }

  .post h4 {
    font-family: var(--display); font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0; text-transform: none;
    margin: 0 0 4px; color: var(--forest-deep); font-weight: 500;
  }
  .post p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .post .post-meta {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-soft); text-align: right;
  }
  .post .post-meta .green { color: #466928; font-weight: 600; }

  .sidebar > div {
    background: rgba(255, 250, 235, 0.4);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    padding: 24px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .sidebar h3 { font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sidebar ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .sidebar ul li { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--rule-soft); }
  .sidebar ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .sidebar .small { font-size: 0.85rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  .access-form { margin-top: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .access-form label {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
    font-family: var(--display); font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .access-form input[type="text"],
  .access-form textarea {
    font-family: var(--body); font-size: 1rem; padding: 8px 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 250, 235, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-soft); border-radius: 2px;
    color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: 0; text-transform: none;
  }
  .access-form input[type="text"]:focus,
  .access-form textarea:focus {
    outline: none; border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(255, 250, 235, 0.9);
  }
  .access-form textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 60px; font-family: var(--body); }
  .access-form button { align-self: flex-start; margin-top: 4px; }

  .concert {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding: 56px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(31, 58, 46, 0.06), rgba(168, 132, 58, 0.04));
    border-top: 1px double var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px double var(--rule);
  }
  .concert-head { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .concert-head h2 { font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; font-size: 2.6rem; }

  .program {
    max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 36px 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 250, 235, 0.7), rgba(217, 195, 136, 0.25));
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px var(--parchment), 0 0 0 9px var(--rule-soft);
    position: relative;
  }
  .program-head { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .program-head .crest-mini { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--gold); }
  .program-head h3 {
    font-family: var(--display); font-style: italic;
    font-size: 2rem; margin: 4px 0; color: var(--forest-deep);
  }
  .program-head .meta { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .program-piece {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr auto;
    gap: 16px; padding: 14px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule-soft);
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .program-piece:first-of-type { border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); margin-top: 16px; }
  .program-piece .pgm-num { font-family: var(--display); color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .program-piece .pgm-title { font-family: var(--display); font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--forest-deep); }
  .program-piece .pgm-title em {
    color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: block; margin-top: 2px; font-family: var(--body);
  }
  .program-piece .pgm-time { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-soft); letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
  .program-foot { text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .rules { margin-top: 56px; padding: 40px 48px; background: rgba(255, 250, 235, 0.4); border: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .rules h2 { font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }
  .rules-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px 48px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .rules-grid h4 { color: var(--oxblood); letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .rules-grid p { font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .hall-grid, .rules-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .post { grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; }
    .post .post-meta { grid-column: 2; text-align: left; }
    .nav { display: none; }
  }
</style>
